    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The FEA model ensemble achieves the required credibility level for Medium model risk. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; 12 of 13 meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by the strength of the quantitative output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96) and the high relevance of the validation scenario to the COU. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU with the understanding that future submissions involving varied loading rates should address the test conditions gap.",
